<item>
            <title>[HBASE-796] Deprecates Text/String methods from HTable and modifies all classes that used Text/String methods so that they use byte[] instead</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-796</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This patch deprecates the text/string methods in HTable and changes all tests/normal methods that use those deprecated methods so that they use the byte[] version of the methods.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12401724">HBASE-796</key>
            <summary>Deprecates Text/String methods from HTable and modifies all classes that used Text/String methods so that they use byte[] instead</summary>
